document_data.name: Fried Cheese
document_data.mainbody: '''Fried cheese''' was a hearty quick meal sometimes served at morningfeast.
document_data.Availability:
*In [[Cormyrean]] trade town of [[Waymoot]], fried cheeses were served at [[The Moon and Stars]] tavern.
*In [[Ormpetarr]], Barony of [[Sespech]], fried cheese was served on thick-crusted [[bread]] as part of a common tavern morningfeast.
*In [[Crimmor]], the Caravan Capital of [[Amn]], smoked [[oyster]]s, fried cheese on [[bread]], and [[pickle]]s were virtually the only meal available at local taverns.
